umn_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From weddings to corporate events to your weekly happy hour, Mark Schaefer is a professional magician that provides a world class close-up magic act for the Seattle metro area. </span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-69 aligncenter\" src=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Line-Under-Fancy-Upsidedown.png\" alt=\"Line-Under-Fancy\" width=\"120\" height=\"20\" /></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#c3924e\" font_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_top=\"0\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><b>CORPORATE FUNCTIONS</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What if you could change “just another day at the office” into an unforgettable experience that will get your company event started off on the right foot?  Mark provides a crisp corporate magic performance that is the perfect entertainment solution for your next corporate event.  Your audience will rave about their experience. </span>\r\n\r\n<a style=\"color: #ffffff;\" href=\"/corporate-events/\" target=\"_blank\">READ MORE &gt;</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><b>WEDDING ENTERTAINMENT</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Looking for unique entertainment for your wedding reception, bachelor or bachelorette party, or rehearsal dinner? Make your special day even more memorable.  The charming magic of Mark Schaefer will leave your guests delighted and will help add a festive atmosphere to your celebration.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><a style=\"color: #ffffff;\" href=\"/private-events/\" target=\"_blank\">READ MORE &gt;</a></span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\"><b> PRIVATE EVENTS\r\n</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Need a fresh idea for a valued holiday, birthday party, fundraiser, or any variety of private event? Turn your event into an experience you and your guests will never forget. Mark is a Seattle magician who provides fun, interactive close-up magic which will amaze your audience and let you live outside the ordinary for an evening.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><a style=\"color: #ffffff;\" href=\"/private-events/\" target=\"_blank\">READ MORE &gt;</a></span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"40\" el_id=\"partner-title\" bg_color=\"#ffffff\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #c6c6c6;\">A FEW OR MARK\'S TRUSTED CLIENTS</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/line-under-2.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-33 aligncenter\" src=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/line-under-2.png\" alt=\"line-under-2\" width=\"35\" height=\"2\" /></a></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" padding_bottom=\"40\" el_id=\"partner-logos\" bg_color=\"#ffffff\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-xs-6\"][vc_single_image image=\"27\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-xs-6\"][vc_single_image image=\"36\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-xs-6\"][vc_single_image image=\"34\" alignment=\"right\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-xs-6\"][vc_single_image image=\"35\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"cards\"][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"56\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"40\" padding_bottom=\"40\" el_id=\"how\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">How does Magic <strong>Fit into My Event?</strong></span></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" padding_bottom=\"40\" el_id=\"icon-hover\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><b>High Quality and Family Friendly</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mark’s magic may be an art but he has it down to a science. His performance quality is high-level, every time. Mark’s magic is always family friendly and professional. He doesn’t use off-color humor or inappropriate, embarrassing magic tricks.</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"75\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>High Quality and Family Friendly</b></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><b>Flexible to Your Needs</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You don’t need a stage, a fancy sound system or equipment - Just Mark!  Professional magic can be used to add fun and entertainment to an event where more than one thing is going on at once.  </span>[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"74\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Flexible to Your Needs</b></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><b>Covers up wait times</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Any time there is a delay and a line-up is formed, Mark can be there to entertain the crowds while they wait, turning a potential frustration into a delight.</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"73\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Covers up wait times</b></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><b>Interactive Entertainment</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At banquet tables or in line, Mark is up close and personal with his audience.  He might ask to borrow your driver’s license, or your wallet might disappear </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(Mark may want to tighten up according to his act)</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.  As a strolling magician, he moves from group to group, engaging with a few people at a time and making everyone feel like a part of the show.</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"76\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Interactive Entertainment</b></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"coin\"][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"57\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" padding_bottom=\"40\" el_id=\"services\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><strong>Services</strong> that Mark Provides</span></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1448019388986{background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\" el_id=\"events\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1448072253504{padding-right: 30px !important;padding-left: 30px !important;}\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Logo-Icon-Gold.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-41\" src=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Logo-Icon-Gold.png\" alt=\"Logo-Icon-Gold\" width=\"69\" height=\"85\" /></a></h3>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">CORPORATE EVENTS</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether you are planning a sales meeting, training seminar, hospitality suite, product launch, or simply a party to show your employees and customers how much you care, </span><b><i>Mark delivers laughter and astonishment every time.  </i></b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you book Mark for an event, you’re getting a corporate magician who knows how to entertain sophisticated adults. </span></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"READ MORE\" color=\"om-theme-color\" size=\"xlg\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Fmarkmagic.wpengine.com%2Fcorporate-events%2F||\" css=\".vc_custom_1448132051339{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1448072276351{padding-right: 30px !important;padding-left: 30px !important;}\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Logo-Icon-Gold.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-41\" src=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Logo-Icon-Gold.png\" alt=\"Logo-Icon-Gold\" width=\"69\" height=\"85\" /></a></h3>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">PRIVATE EVENTS</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As an award-winning private party magician, Mark Schaefer provides fun and amazing private party entertainment that all of your family and friends will love. Mark has years of experience performing and delighting clients at private parties. From intimate dinner parties to large family celebrations, this is a show that will leave your guests talking.</span></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"READ MORE\" color=\"om-theme-color\" size=\"xlg\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Fmarkmagic.wpengine.com%2Fcorporate-events%2F||\" css=\".vc_custom_1448132056930{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"40\" padding_bottom=\"40\" el_id=\"why\" bg_color=\"#ffffff\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1447967396512{margin-top: 20px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1>What makes Mark\'s Magic<strong> Unique</strong></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_tta_accordion active_section=\"544\" collapsible_all=\"true\"][vc_tta_section title=\"Amazing Private Party Entertainment\" tab_id=\"1447302533825-be1dc3b4-83a5\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is high-class sleight-of-hand for sophisticated audiences. Your guests will be impressed!</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Professional Image\" tab_id=\"1447302533984-de999d3d-7b73\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I’m always professional and polite, so you’ll never have to worry about off-color humor or embarrassing situations.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Reliable\" tab_id=\"1447355693122-6e67b073-61c9\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">No flakiness here.  Mark’s magic may be an art but he has it down to a science.  His performance quality is high-level, every time.  He is always punctual and will meet the needs of your event’s time format.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Works in Any Venue\" tab_id=\"1447355696115-ab1979c1-4600\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I’ve performed in living rooms, country clubs, and on chartered boats. I know how to tailor my performances to suit your unique venue and atmosphere.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Stress Free\" tab_id=\"1447355732198-b329647e-d36e\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Unlike other private party magicians, my magic is hassle-free. There’s no lighting, sound, or stage requirements. It couldn’t be easier!</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][vc_btn title=\"READ REVIEWS\" style=\"outline\" color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"left\" custom_color=\"#474747\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" delimiter=\"rarr\" css_animation=\"zoom-in\" css=\".vc_custom_1447967467837{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 30px !important;background-color: #c3924e !important;}\" css_animation_delay=\"1\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1448078511808{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]\r\n<h1>Contact <strong>Mark</strong> Today!</h1>\r\nMark will get back to you within a business day.[/vc_column_text][gravityform id=\"2\" title=\"false\" description=\"false\" ajax=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"40\" bg_color=\"#f1f1f1\" padding_bottom=\"40\" el_id=\"testimonials\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1447355432414{margin-bottom: -14px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #c6c6c6;\">TESTIMONIALS</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/line-under-2.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-33 aligncenter\" src=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/line-under-2.png\" alt=\"line-under-2\" width=\"35\" height=\"2\" /></a></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Others Who have <strong>Experienced the Magic</strong></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][om_testimonials category=\"3\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][om_testimonials mode=\"list\" category=\"3\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][om_testimonials mode=\"list\" category=\"3\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" parallax=\"content-moving\" css=\".vc_custom_1434539542642{padding-top: 100px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;background-color: #587199 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#c3924e\" padding_top=\"40\" padding_bottom=\"40\" el_id=\"get-started\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Ready to Start the Conversation? Call Mark at 949-275-3272\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:25|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff|line_height:1\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1448163300919{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id=\"lightbox-form\"][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1447841825281{background-color: #c3924e !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1>Contact <strong>Mark</strong> Today!</h1>\r\nMark will get back to you within a business day.[/vc_column_text][gravityform id=\"1\" title=\"false\" description=\"false\" ajax=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2015-11-22 03:35:02','2015-11-22 03:35:02','',0,'http://markmagic.wpengine.com/?page_id=5',0,'page','',0),(6,2,'2015-11-06 21:46:35','2015-11-06 21:46:35','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#c5a781\" font_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_top=\"40\" padding_bottom=\"40\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"48\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">More than Entertainment - <strong>A</strong><b>n Experience!</b></span></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-69 aligncenter\" src=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Line-Under-Fancy-Upsidedown.png\" alt=\"Line-Under-Fancy\" width=\"120\" height=\"20\" /></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><b>MISSION</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">My mission is to provide a clean, interactive magic experience that will make guests feel like the magic actually “happened to them” as opposed to merely being part of the audience. I really engage with the audience, forming a personal connection.  This tends to deepen their appreciation for my performance. My most common feedback is that people come back over to see \"me\" and not just what I do with the magic.</span>\r\n<h3><b>PERSONAL STORY</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I began my magic career in Los Angeles in 2000, I was able to hone my craft as a stage magician before moving on to sleight of hand and close-up magic. I have been fascinated with this art ever since, which is widely considered the purest form of magic.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since beginning his career, Mark has won</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> ___, ___, ___.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">  He has been featured on </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">____.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">  He was involved with </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">_____.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mark now provides a world-class close-up magic, incorporating card and coin tricks, everyday objects, and mentalism into his act.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"40\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #c6c6c6;\">A FEW OR MARK\'S TRUSTED CLIENTS</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/line-under-2.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-33 aligncenter\" src=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/line-under-2.png\" alt=\"line-under-2\" width=\"35\" height=\"2\" /></a></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" padding_bottom=\"40\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"27\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"36\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"34\" alignment=\"right\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"35\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding_top=\"40\" padding_bottom=\"40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1448139632921{margin-top: 30px !important;}\"]\r\n<h1>How I Can Help\r\n<strong>Your Event be a Success</strong></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_tta_accordion active_section=\"544\" collapsible_all=\"true\"][vc_tta_section title=\"Corporate/Professional Event Focused\" tab_id=\"1447302533825-be1dc3b4-83a57f1f-4844e303-75a3\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I’ve developed the experience to be able to tailor my performance depending on how your meeting flows, the audience, and the timeframe.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Hilarity and Amazement Guaranteed\" tab_id=\"1447302533984-de999d3d-7b737f1f-4844e303-75a3\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">XYZ Corp, ACME, and ABC Co.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> are all repeat customers of mine.  </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Professional Attitude\" tab_id=\"1447355693122-6e67b073-61c97f1f-4844e303-75a3\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I buck the trend that professional entertainers are flakes, which is why I am so often hired as a corporate entertainer. I know how important your event is to you and will do everything in my power to ensure it runs smoothly.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Committed to Making You Look Good\" tab_id=\"1447355696115-ab1979c1-46007f1f-4844e303-75a3\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">My performance centers around your event going seamlessly.  I take the pressure off you during wait times or slow moments - I’ll entertain the masses which frees you up to handle pressing logistics during your event.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Complements Your Private Party\" tab_id=\"1447355732198-b329647e-d36e7f1f-4844e303-75a3\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Likely your party commemorates some special occasion.  Having a strolling magician complements your event but my magic doesn’t take center stage (unless you want it to!). I help create lasting memories of how amazing the event was but you are ultimately the hero of the day.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][vc_btn title=\"READ REVIEWS\" style=\"outline\" color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"left\" custom_color=\"#474747\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" delimiter=\"rarr\" css_animation=\"zoom-in\" css=\".vc_custom_1447357260013{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;background-color: #c3924e !important;}\" css_animation_delay=\"1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Contact <strong>Mark</strong> Today!</span></h1>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Mark will get back to you within a business day.</span>[/vc_column_text][gravityform id=\"2\" title=\"false\" description=\"false\" ajax=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"40\" bg_color=\"#f1f1f1\" padding_bottom=\"40\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1447355432414{margin-bottom: -14px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #c6c6c6;\">TESTIMONIALS</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/line-under-2.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-33 aligncenter\" src=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/line-under-2.png\" alt=\"line-under-2\" width=\"35\" height=\"2\" /></a></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Others Who have <strong>Experienced the Magic</strong></span></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][om_testimonials category=\"3\"][/vc_