5/11/Line-Under-Fancy-Upsidedown.png\" alt=\"Line-Under-Fancy\" width=\"120\" height=\"20\" /></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#c3924e\" font_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_top=\"0\" padding_bottom=\"0\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Your choice of corporate event entertainment is an opportunity for your organization to maintain the status quo, move forward, or even backward. By adding Mark as part of your corporate event entertainment, you open up the possibility for employees to let their guard down, for co-workers to bond around a common experience.  Hosting a professional magician can promote a creative spirit in your office.</span>\r\n\r\nMark Schaefer is an experienced corporate magician whose performances combine charm, sophisticated sleight of hand, and audience participation.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His years of experience entertaining at business events ensure he knows how to make you and your company look good.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From sales meetings to product launches, </span><span style=\"color: #faafaf;\"><a style=\"color: #faafaf;\" href=\"http://arthurtrace.com/trade-show-magician/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">trade shows</span></a></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to client appreciation soirees and more, Mark can tailor his close-up and/ or stage magic to deliver your message in an entertaining and impactful way. Or, he can simply wow your VIPs and make sure everyone is having a great time.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#c3924e\" font_color=\"#ffffff\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][om_moving_box content_type=\"icon\" animation=\"pulse\" icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-angle-down\" color=\"white\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/