</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Bond Around a Common Experience.\" tab_id=\"1447355693122-6e67b073-61c97f1f-4844\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Magic provides an opportunity for people to bond around a common experience. Co-workers who you never thought could become friends now have something to talk about.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Provoke Wonderment\" tab_id=\"1447355696115-ab1979c1-46007f1f-4844\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mark’s mentalism and mind-reading techniques are mystifying and will provoke wonderment among your colleagues. They can really throw off the right-brained thinkers in your office!</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Talk of the Office\" tab_id=\"1447355732198-b329647e-d36e7f1f-4844\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mark’s performance will be the talk of the office well beyond the event itself.  Everyone will congratulate you on your choice of entertainment!</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][vc_btn title=\"READ REVIEWS\" style=\"outline\" color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"left\" custom_color=\"#474747\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" delimiter=\"rarr\" css_animation=\"zoom-in\" css=\".vc_custom_1448131333314{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 30px !important;background-color: #c3924e !important;}\" css_animation_delay=\"1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Contact <strong>Mark</strong> Today!</span></h1>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Mark will get back to you within a business day.</span>[/vc_column_text][gravityform id=\"2\" title=\"false\" description=\"false\" ajax=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"40\" bg_color=\"#f1f1f1\" padding_bottom=\"40\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1447355432414{margin-