 a business day.[/vc_column_text][gravityform id=\"1\" title=\"false\" description=\"false\" ajax=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Corporate Events','','publish','closed','closed','','corporate-events','','','2015-11-25 21:06:39','2015-11-25 21:06:39','',0,'http://markmagic.wpengine.com/?page_id=7',0,'page','',0),(8,2,'2015-11-06 21:47:08','2015-11-06 21:47:08','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#c3924e\" font_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_top=\"20\" padding_bottom=\"0\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When ordinary <strong>just won\'t cut it</strong>.</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-69 aligncenter\" src=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Line-Under-Fancy-Upsidedown.png\" alt=\"Line-Under-Fancy\" width=\"120\" height=\"20\" /></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#c3924e\" font_color=\"#ffffff\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sometimes you need that dynamic element to change the nature of your private party or event - to make it even more special, to make it to stand out. You could choose a comedian, hire a band, or just serve more alcohol.  But why choose a professional magician?</span>\r\n\r\nThe biggest benefit of adding Mark’s performance to an event is how flexible it can be. You don’t need any special equipment or set-up. Just Mark![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Often, professional magic is used to add fun and entertainment to an event where more than one thing is going on at once. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sophisticated close-up magic takes place right in the guests\' hands - it gets them excited to be a part of the entire event. </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#c392