 provides a world class close-up magic act for the Seattle metro area. </span></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-69 aligncenter\" src=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Line-Under-Fancy-Upsidedown.png\" alt=\"Line-Under-Fancy\" width=\"120\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#c3924e\" font_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_top=\"0\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3><b>CORPORATE FUNCTIONS</b></h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What if you could change “just another day at the office” into an unforgettable experience that will get your company event started off on the right foot?  Mark provides a crisp corporate magic performance that is the perfect entertainment solution for your next corporate event.  Your audience will rave about their experience. </span>\n\n<a style=\"color: #ffffff;\" href=\"/corporate-events/\" target=\"_blank\">READ MORE &gt;</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3><b>WEDDING ENTERTAINMENT</b></h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Looking for unique entertainment for your wedding reception, bachelor or bachelorette party, or rehearsal dinner? Make your special day even more memorable.  The charming magic of Mark Schaefer will leave your guests delighted and will help add a festive atmosphere to your celebration.</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><a style=\"color: #ffffff;\" href=\"/private-events/\" target=\"_blank\">READ MORE &gt;</a></span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\"><b> PRIVATE EVENTS\n</b></h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Need a fresh idea for a valued holiday, birthday party, fundraiser, or any variety of private event? Turn your event into an experience you and your guests will never forget. Mark is a Seattle magician who provides fun, interactive close-up magic which will amaze your audience and let you live outside the ordinary for an evening.</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><a style=\"color: #ffffff;\" href=\"/private-events/\" target=\"_blank\">READ MORE &gt;</a></span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"40\" el_id=\"partner-title\" bg_color=\"#ffffff\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #c6c6c6;\">A FEW OR MARK\'S TRUSTED CLIENTS</span></strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/line-under-2.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-33 aligncenter\" src=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/line-under-2.png\" alt=\"line-under-2\" width=\"35\" height=\"2\" /></a></p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" padding_bottom=\"40\" el_id=\"partner-logos\" bg_color=\"#ffffff\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-xs-6\"][vc_single_image image=\"27\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-xs-6\"][vc_single_image image=\"36\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-xs-6\"][vc_single_image image=\"34\" alignment=\"right\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-xs-6\"][vc_single_image image=\"35\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"cards\"][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"56\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"40\" padding_bottom=\"40\" el_id=\"how\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">How does Magic <strong>Fit into My Event?</strong></span></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" padding_bottom=\"40\" el_id=\"icon-hover\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3><b>High Quality and Family Friendly</b></h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mark’s magic may be an art but he has it down to a science. His performance quality is high-level, every time. Mark’s magic is always family friendly and professional. He doesn’t use off-color humor or inappropriate, embarrassing magic tricks.</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"75\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>High Quality and Family Friendly</b></p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3><b>Flexible to Your Needs</b></h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You don’t need a stage, a fancy sound system or equipment - Just Mark!  Professional magic can be used to add fun and entertainment to an event where more than one thing is going on at once.  </span>[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"74\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Flexible to Your Needs</b></p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3><b>Covers up wait times</b></h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Any time there is a delay and a line-up is formed, Mark can be there to entertain the crowds while they wait, turning a potential frustration into a delight.</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"73\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Covers up wait times</b></p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3><b>Interactive Entertainment</b></h3>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At banquet tables or in line, Mark is up close and personal with his audience.  He might ask to borrow your driver’s license, or your wallet might disappear </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(Mark may want to tighten up according to his act)</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.  As a strolling magician, he moves from group to group, engaging with a few people at a time and making everyone feel like a part of the show.</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"76\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Interactive Entertainment</b></p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"coin\"][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"57\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" padding_bottom=\"40\" el_id=\"services\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><strong>Services</strong> that Mark Provides</span></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1448019388986{background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\" el_id=\"events\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1448072253504{padding-right: 30px !important;padding-left: 30px !important;}\"]\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Logo-Icon-Gold.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-41\" src=\"http://markmagic.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Logo-Icon-Gold.png\" alt=\"Logo-Icon-Gold\" width=\"69\" height=\"85\" /></a></h3>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">CORPORATE EVENTS</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether you are planning a sales meeting, training seminar, hospitality suite, product launch, or simply a party to show your employees and customers how much you care, </span><b><i>Mark delivers laughter and astonishment every time.  </i></b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you book Mark for an event, you’re getting a corporate magician who knows how to entertain sophisticated adults. </span></p>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"READ MORE\" color=\"om-theme-color\" size=\"xlg\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Fmarkmagic.wpengi