nd, or just serve more alcohol.  But why choose a professional magician?</span>\n\nThe biggest benefit of adding Mark’s performance to an event is how flexible it can be. You don’t need any special equipment or set-up. Just Mark![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Often, professional magic is used to add fun and entertainment to an event where more than one thing is going on at once. Sophisticated close-up magic takes place right in the guests\' hands - it gets them excited to be a part of the entire event. </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#c3924e\" font_color=\"#ffffff\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][om_moving_box content_type=\"icon\" animation=\"pulse\" icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-angle-down\" color=\"white\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"40\" bg_color=\"#f1f1f1\" padding_bottom=\"-20\"][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1448425474221{margin-bottom: -40px !important;}\"]\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><strong>Any Venue</strong> Any Size</span></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"0\" bg_color=\"#f1f1f1\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Mark’s performance can accommodate any number of guests and any size venue. He is an excellent choice as a birthday party magician or wedding magician. In addition, he has performed at:</h3>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"40\" bg_color=\"#f1f1f1\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1448137377692{margin-left: 30px !important;}\"]\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt; Community events</span></h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt; </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Religious events</span></h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt; Dances</span></h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt; Banquets</span></h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt; Fundraisers</span></h4>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1448137414568{margin-left: 30px !important;}\"]\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt; </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rehearsal dinners</span></h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt; Bachelor parties</span></h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt; Bachelorette parties</span></h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt; </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Christmas Parties</span></h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt; </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Halloween Parties</span></h4>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding_top=\"40\" padding_bottom=\"40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1448130572996{margin-top: 20px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\n<h1>Making Your Event a <strong>Success</strong></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_tta_accordion active_section=\"\" collapsible_all=\"true\"][vc_tta_section title=\"Interactive Experience\" tab_id=\"1447302533825-be1dc3b4-83a57f1f-48449cf6-e1d1\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Magic is ideal at cocktail receptions and banquet events, and as a lead-in to a</span><a href=\"http://kostyakimlat.com/group-show.html\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> group show</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Your guests will love the </span><b><i>one-on-one experience</i></b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and the extra attention they get from Mark.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Breaks the Ice\" tab_id=\"1447302533984-de999d3d-7b737f1f-48449cf6-e1d1\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Magic is one of the best ways to </span><b><i>break the ice</i></b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and get your guests laughing, smiling and having fun! </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Covers up Wait Times\" tab_id=\"1447355693122-6e67b073-61c97f1f-48449cf6-e1d1\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mark’s performance easily </span><b><i>covers up wait times</i></b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Any time there is a delay or transition time at your event, Mark entertains the crowds while they wait, turning a potential point of frustration into quite possibly the biggest hit of the evening.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Keeps Hungry Guests at Bay\" tab_id=\"1447355696115-ab1979c1-46007f1f-48449cf6-e1d1\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Banquet Dinners: </span><b><i>Keeps hungry guests at bay. </i></b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The larger the crowd, the more waiting there is at dinner time. Having Mark visit your table can really make the time fly by!</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Just Different\" tab_id=\"1447355732198-b329647e-d36e7f1f-48449cf6-e1d1\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mark’s Magic is </span><b><i>just different</i></b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. It’s totally unlike what we experience every day, where the law of cause and effect reigns. You and your guests will be both captivated and perplexed by his performance, always wanting to know how he pulled off his last trick.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][vc_btn title=\"RE